---
layout: base.njk
title: "Kontakt"
description: "Kontakt Emil Salzer for bookinger, foredrag, presse og øvrige henvendelser."
canonical: "https://emilsalzer.dk/kontakt/"
ogTitle: "Kontakt — Emil Salzer"
ogDescription: "Book foredrag, oplæsning eller kontakt Emil Salzer."
ogUrl: "https://emilsalzer.dk/kontakt/"
ogImage: "https://emilsalzer.dk/assets/images/kontakt-1.jpg"
extraHead: |
  <style>
      .contact-hero {
          position: relative;
          min-height: 90vh;
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          justify-content: center;
          overflow: hidden;
      }
      .contact-hero-bg {
          position: absolute;
          top: 0; left: 0;
          width: 100%; height: 100%;
          object-fit: cover;
          object-position: center;
          filter: grayscale(100%);
      }

      .contact-form-wrapper {
          position: relative;
          z-index: 2;
          padding: 80px 64px;
          max-width: 560px;
          margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .contact-form-wrapper h1 {
          font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 64px);
          font-weight: 700;
          margin-bottom: 12px;
          line-height: 1.1;
          color: var(--black);
      }
      .contact-form-wrapper .subtitle {
          font-size: 16px;
          color: var(--black);
          font-weight: 700;
          margin-bottom: 40px;
          line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .form-group { margin-bottom: 24px; }
      .form-group label {
          display: block;
          font-style: italic;
          font-size: 15px;
          color: #000;
          margin-bottom: 6px;
      }
      .form-group input,
      .form-group textarea {
          width: 100%;
          border: none;
          border-bottom: 1px solid var(--black);
          padding: 8px 0;
          font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
          font-size: 16px;
          background: transparent;
          color: var(--black);
          outline: none;
          transition: border-color 0.2s;
      }
      .form-group input:focus,
      .form-group textarea:focus {
          border-bottom-color: #000;
      }
      .form-group textarea {
          resize: vertical;
          min-height: 80px;
      }
      .form-row {
          display: grid;
          grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
          gap: 24px;
      }

      .form-submit {
          display: inline-block;
          padding: 14px 48px;
          background: var(--black);
          color: var(--white);
          border: none;
          font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
          font-size: 15px;
          font-weight: 700;
          letter-spacing: 0.5px;
          cursor: pointer;
          transition: opacity 0.2s;
          margin-top: 8px;
      }
      .form-submit:hover { opacity: 0.8; }

      .success-message {
          display: none;
          padding: 20px;
          background: var(--light-grey);
          text-align: center;
          font-size: 16px;
          margin-top: 20px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 900px) {
          .contact-form-wrapper { padding: 48px 24px; }
          .contact-hero { min-height: 80vh; }
          .contact-hero-bg { opacity: 0.3; }
          .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      }
  </style>
extraScripts: |
  <script>
  if (window.location.hash === '#tak') {
      document.getElementById('contactForm').style.display = 'none';
      document.getElementById('successMsg').style.display = 'block';
  }
  </script>
---

<section class="contact-hero">
    <img src="/assets/images/kontakt-1.jpg" alt="Emil Salzer" class="contact-hero-bg" loading="eager">
    <div class="contact-form-wrapper">
        <h1>Kontakt Emil.</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Vil du booke oplæsning, foredrag eller har en anden forespørgsel, så skriv her:</p>

        <form action="https://formspree.io/f/xaqpaepv" method="POST" id="contactForm">
            <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="Henvendelse via emilsalzer.dk">
            <input type="hidden" name="_next" value="https://emilsalzer.dk/kontakt/#tak">

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="name">Navn</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="org">Organisation</label>
                <input type="text" id="org" name="organisation">
            </div>

            <div class="form-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="email">E-mail</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="phone">Telefon</label>
                    <input type="tel" id="phone" name="telefon">
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="message">Evt. kommentar</label>
                <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="3"></textarea>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="form-submit">Send</button>
        </form>

        <div class="success-message" id="successMsg">
            Tak for din henvendelse. Emil vender tilbage hurtigst muligt.
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
